*Momče* je izabralo da ode na more. (The boy chose to go to the sea.)

*Momče* je uživalo u odmoru. (The boy was enjoying the vacation.)

*Momčeta* su igrala u dvorištu. (The boys were playing in the yard.)

*Momčad* je odigrala zanimljiv fudbalski meč. (The team played an interesting football match.)

*Momče* je zaplakalo zbog gubitka najboljeg prijatelja. (The boy cried because of the loss of his best friend.)